body:
Easy, 100% guaranteed way of getting banned! If you've ever wanted to get banned for whatever reason, just do this.

Don't unban me please.

I saw a post about not being able to link to the video and wanted to test it out

Edit: Let me copy over the notification. And yeah, like they said, they ban alts. My other account @_User got banned too.

I can't view my own profile and can't even edit my own posts. Even reddit lets you do that. (Reddit allows you to edit posts when you're banned in case you've ever posted anything you don't want others to see anymore, like personal information.) I can still do GM stuff apparently (I think that's intended). I was able to yank and kick this post.

Edit 2: Upvoting posts seems to work, but if I try to upvote a comment, it gives a popup message saying "Unable to vote at this time. Please try again later."

***

**Ruqqus Notification**

ruqqus · 4 minutes ago

Your Ruqqus account has been suspended for 1 day for the following reason:

>Too much spam!

***

\- sfrohne
